               <head>Treatise on arithmetic</head>
               <msContents>
                  <summary>1 copy of Lubāb al-ḥiṣāb by ʿAbd al-Karīm ibn Maḥmūd</summary>
                  <msItem class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2010101033 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh85068424 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh85007164" n="1" xml:id="Uk_IO_Islamic_4642-item1">
                     <author>
                        <persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" type="supplied" key="person_f7017"> ʿAbd al-Karīm ibn Maḥmūd</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="per" type="supplied" key="person_f7017">عبد الكريم ابن محمود</persName>
                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="work_22049">Lubāb al-ḥiṣāb</title>
                     <title xml:lang="per" key="work_22049">لباب الحساب</title>
                     <note>
                        <p>Brief treatise on arithmetic based on the <title>Khulāṣat al-ḥisāb</title> of <persName key="viaf_27052262" role="ant">Bahāʾ al-Dīn ʿĀmilī</persName> and other commentaries, composed by <persName key="person_f7017" role="aut">ʿAbd al-Karīm ibn Maḥmūd</persName> with the assistance of his own teacher, <persName key="person_f7028" role="ctb">ʿAbd al-Raḥīm Bījāpūrī</persName>
                        </p>
                        <p>Although the work talks of containing a muqaddimah and eight bāb, the present volume consists only of the muqaddimah </p>
                        <p>
                           <persName key="viaf_79056967" role="cataloguer">Arberry</persName> suggests this may be the author's autograph 
                        </p>
                        <p>Not dated </p>
                     </note>
